verse.lines:
{lang-eng}Begin the day with God!
He is thy sun and day;
His is the radiance of thy dawn,
To Him commit thy way.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Sing a new song at morn!
Join the glad woods and hills;
Join the fresh winds and seas and plains,
Join the bright flowers and rills.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Sing thy first song to God
Not to thy fellow man;
Not to the creatures of His hand,
But to the glorious One.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Take thy first walk with God!
Let Him go forth with thee;
By stream or sea or mountain path,
Seek still His company.{/lang-eng}

{lang-eng}Thy first transaction be
With God Himself above;
So shall thy business prosper well,
And all the day be love.{/lang-eng}
